The Freeze service will allow you to limit access to your credit history to credit institutions (users of the KIAC credit bureau). To activate the Freeze service, you need to activate the SMS notification service. With the connected SMS notification and Freeze service, if a credit institution tries to obtain a credit history, you will receive an SMS notification about this. The exception is existing agreements, according to LRU No. 301 dated 10/04/2011, a credit institution can study your credit history based on your consent, which is active until the term of the agreement. The Freeze service is activated for an unlimited period. Disconnecting the service is free.
